metadata.name: CARE OUT OF INSIDE
metadata.description:
This is the first work of the collection "CARE OF".

It is about physical and emotional connection, a sense of safeness and sense of gratefulness.

All of us, unwittingly, turn out to be connected to each other. Connected by common pain and common love. 
And all I am talking about trough this work - is about taking care of yourself, teaching of how to love yourself.
